<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div style="border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none; border-right:none; padding:1.0pt 0in 1.0pt 0in">
<p style="border:none; padding:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Necrotizing Fasciitis</span></span></b></span></span></span></p>
</div>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Background</span></span></span> </span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Infection</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"> of the deeper soft tissues that causes necrosis along the muscle fascia and overlying subcutaneous fat that is rapidly progressive and lethal if not addressed</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Clinical cues include pain out of proportion to exam, hemorrhagic bullae</span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:25px; text-indent:-9.35pt"> </p>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Evaluation</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">/Management</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
